udhr"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-gP","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":19124,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/12\/five-pillars-and-family-ties\/","url_meta":{"origin":1043,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Perform the five pillars, be kind to family","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 12, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Ayyub reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cTell me what I can do to enter Paradise and avoid Hellfire.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cWorship Allah and do not associate anything with Him, perform the prayer, give in charity, and keep\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7537,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/03\/family-ties-increase-wealth-life\/","url_meta":{"origin":1043,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Rahim: Good relations with family increase wealth, extend life","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik\u00a0reported: The\u00a0Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever is pleased to have his provision expanded and his life span extended, let him keep good relations with his family.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2067, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2557 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19116,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/12\/womb-under-arsh-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":1043,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Family: Bond of kinship under Throne of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 12, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe bond of family is suspended from the Throne, and it says: Whoever upholds me, Allah will uphold him. Whoever severs me, Allah will sever him.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5989, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2555 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19119,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/12\/maintain-relations-kuffar-family\/","url_meta":{"origin":1043,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Family: The Prophet does not cut off unbelieving relatives","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 12, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"'Amr ibn al-\u2018As reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the relatives\u00a0of my father are not my allies. Verily, only Allah and the righteous believers are my allies. Yet, they have the bonds of kinship and I will uphold their family ties.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5990,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18973,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/03\/gossiper-not-enter-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":1043,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Namimah: Gossip-monger will not enter Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 3, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe gossiper will not enter Paradise.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6056, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 105 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062d\u064f\u0630\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0629 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u062f\u0652\u062e\u064f\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u062a\u0651\u064e\u0627\u062a\u064c 6056 \u0635\u062d\u064a\u062d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":943,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/07\/23\/spending-on-your-family-sadaqah\/","url_meta":{"origin":1043,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqah: Spending on your family is an act of charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 23, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Mas'ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"If a Muslim spends on his family seeki